			<li class=""><a href="javascript:void(0);" id="hint-on-task"
			rel="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" title="Show Hints on how to exploit this view."><i
					class="icon-large  icon-comments "></i></a></li>
		
		<li class=""><a href="javascript:void(0);" id="help-on-task"
			rel="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" title="Show Help and Hints on how to use this view."><i
